SUBST	- rule, simultaneous substitution using a pattern

SUBST: (thm * term)list -> form -> thm -> thm
	       xi	   A(xi)



Simultaneous Substitution

	ti == ui    A(ti)
    -------------------------
	    A(ui)

The formula A(xi) serves as a template to control the subtitution;
the variables xi mark the places where substitution should occur.
